{"tid":2116100,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚耀宗認為政府不應排除將立法會選舉延期","createTime":"2020-07-20T03:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T05:10:02.000Z","uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ee64eba4de857d3e8610028ee79b378d216fc2c7","tid":2116100,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T03:01:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全國人大常委、民建聯會務顧問譚耀宗認為，疫情嚴峻，政府不應排除將立法會換屆選舉延期。<br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗說，現時距離選舉有50多天時間，政府不能保證疫情一定受控，如疫情持續，在選舉時有多人聚集，擔心選舉後又有另一波爆發。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538782-20200720.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538782-20200720.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zRnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=862df736\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538782-20200720.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=845bd02e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538782-20200720.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"0dfcaf90cde848e242eefc2856599fda47ea6a65","tid":2116100,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T03:03:13.000Z","msg":"協商決定算啦"},{"pid":"22e2689a48b9d4b29347f360eb1604beb6bcbbad","tid":2116100,"uid":67325,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T03:03:41.000Z","msg":"係囉，咁未無咗好多掌心雷囉"},{"pid":"69f80c1a8dd4cb21d8dcbd7aa3fd49a02ee2f8f3","tid":2116100,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T03:04:07.000Z","msg":"出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f38810a91d89084be78271e5a7ca1dda0d4604","tid":2116100,"uid":166474,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T03:05:22.000Z","msg":"驚班廢老唔敢出黎投票, 同埋長期定居大陸班人落黎要隔離14日, 要安排佢地食宿好重皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgm